World


The map shows the number of daily, weekly and monthly new cases over time. The line running along below the map indicates the trend over time.

Interact with the map:

  • Look at weekly and monthly data by clicking WEEK or MONTH on the top left.

  • Pause the timeline below the map and hover over the points for more info.

  • Move the vertical line on the timeline to see a specific date.

  • Zoom in and out using the tools on the top right.



Sources

  • World SARS-CoV-2 data (new cases): Our World in Data
